Lloyds's Capper Says Non-Financial Stocks `More Robust'

-- B y  
-- 
2011-09-15T12:34:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-15/lloyds-s-capper-says-non-financial-stocks-more-robust-video.html
Alan Capper, managing director at 
Lloyds TSB Corporate Markets, discusses the European sovereign 
debt crisis and the global financial system three years after 
the collapse of Lehman Brothers Holdings Inc.  He speaks with Maryam Nemazee on Bloomberg Television's 
"The Pulse." (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 04:40
 